00:00:13.232 --> 00:00:17.112
Hi! Welcome to Aha Emi Ruchi!

00:00:32.250 --> 00:00:38.077
What are going to cook?
Coconut Khichdi

00:00:48.138 --> 00:00:50.622
Ingredients required to make Coconut Khichdi

00:00:51.077 --> 00:00:58.836
Grated Coconut, Peanuts, Sugar, Raisins, Cashews, Cardamom, Oil

00:01:10.342 --> 00:01:16.503
Light the stove

00:01:24.607 --> 00:01:40.457
Take a pot and heat some oil

00:02:00.512 --> 00:02:13.728
We're using 250 gm of sugar for two coconuts used

00:02:14.138 --> 00:02:30.034
Add the sugar and add a little water to make a syrup

00:02:49.462 --> 00:03:07.683
Fry the two grated coconuts in oil lightly, for a little while before using

00:03:27.034 --> 00:03:34.265
Add the grated coconut

00:04:10.666 --> 00:04:17.725
We need to use roasted peanuts

00:04:20.569 --> 00:04:26.033
Add the roasted peanuts

00:04:57.255 --> 00:05:07.182
Take a plate and grease it up with some oil and
 then transfer the coconut khichdi onto it

00:05:21.570 --> 00:05:38.463
Take the sweet coconut khichdi onto the plate and level it out

00:05:42.342 --> 00:05:58.601
Garnish with some raisins and cashews

00:06:02.379 --> 00:06:08.716
Sprinkle some cardamom powder over the khichdi

